# Django使用文档

## 安装

```batch
pip install django
```

## 项目

### 创建项目

- 使用命令行
  
  ```batch
  django-admin startproject ProjectName
  ```

- 使用PyCharm（专业版)
  
  PyCharm生成的项目会额外生成templates目录
  
  settings.py中会额外增加一行templates配置
  
  ```python
  'DIRS': [os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'templates')]
  ```
  
  存在此配置时，将优先从项目根目录的templates中寻找模板

### 启动项目

- 命令行启动
  
  ```batch
  python manage.py runserver
  ```

- PyCharm启动（专业版）
  
  需通过PyCharm创建Django项目

### 默认项目文件

```
django
│  manage.py        [项目管理，启动项目、创建app、数据管理]
│
├─.idea
│  │  .gitignore
│  │  django.iml
│  │  misc.xml
│  │  modules.xml
│  │  workspace.xml
│  │
│  └─inspectionProfiles
│          profiles_settings.xml
│
└─django
        settings.py    [项目配置文件，常用]

        asgi.py        [接收网络请求，无需改动]
        wsgi.py        [接收网络请求，无需改动]
        __init__.py
```

## APP (Module)

Django中以app管理项目

### app创建

```batch
python manage.py startapp APP名
```

```
APP
│  admin.py        [默认后台管理]
│  apps.py         [app启动]
│  models.py       [对数据库操作，常用]
│  tests.py        [单元测试]
│  views.py        [函数，常用]
│  __init__.py
│
└─migrations
        __init__.py
```

### 静态文件

![image](data:image/png;base64,)

```html

<link rel="stylesheet" href="{% static 'css/bootstrap.css' %}">

<script src="{% static 'js/bootstrap.js' %}"></script>
```

### 模板

settings.py 中配置

如不设置路径，默认从根目录到APP的templates文件夹中顺序查找对应模板文件

![image](data:image/png;base64,)

#### 模板的继承

可设定多个块，使用不同名字区分

```html
{% block 块名 %}{% endblock %}     [占位，可做内容替换]
```

```html
# layout.html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<header></header>
<body>
{% block content %}
{% endblock %}
</body>
<footer></footer>


# index.html

{% extends 'layout.html' %}           [引入layout模板]

{% block content %}                   [替换到layout模板占位位置]
    <div class="container">
        ...
    </div>
{% endblock %}
```

#### ForeignKey

对于使用ForeignKey创建的数据列，django会自动添加_id

如创建depart，则自动生成depart_id，depart用来获取对应表中的参数

```py
depart = models.ForeignKey(to="Department", to_field="dep_code", on_delete=models.CASCADE),
```

```py
print(user.depart_id)
1

print(user.depart.title)
IT
```

+ on_delete

```
CASCADE：        删除该数据时，删除与之关联的所有数据；
PROTECT：        删除该数据时，采取保护机制，抛出错误：即不删除关联数据；
SET_NULL：       只有当null=True才将关联数据置空；
SET_DEFAULT：    设置默认值；
SET()：          设定命令或函数；
DO_NOTHING：     无动作
```

Form与ModelForm，Form建议用于非数据库操作，ModelForm用于对数据库操作

#Form  
class UserForm(forms.Form):
    name = models.CharField(max_length=32)
    password = models.CharField(max_length=64)
    age = models.IntegerField()

#ModelForm（推荐）
class UserForm(forms.ModelForm):
    class Meta:
        model = models.UserInfo
        fields = ["name", "password", "age"]

class user_add(request):

#### 属性样式

添加widgets，指定属性

```py
class UserForm(forms.ModelForm):
    name = forms.CharField(
        min_length = 3,
        label = "用户名",
        widget = forms.TextInput(attrs={"class": "form-control"})
    )
    class Meta:
        model = models.UserInfo
        fields = ["name", "password", "age"]
```

```py
class UserForm(forms.ModelForm):
    class Meta:
        model = models.UserInfo
        fields = ["name", "password", "age"]

        widgets = {
            "name": forms.TextInput(attrs={"class": "form-control"}),
            "password": forms.PasswordInput(attrs={"class": "form-control"}),
            "age": forms.NumberInput(attrs={"class": "form-control"}),
        }
```

可通过重新定义init方法进行循环添加

```py
class UserForm(forms.ModelForm):
    class Meta:
        model = models.UserInfo
        fields = ["name", "password", "age"]

    def __init__(self, *args, **kwargs):
        super().__init__(*args, **kwargs)
        for name, field in self.fields.items():
            field.widget.attrs = {"class": "form-control"}
```

### 提交数据

```py
#(instance=user)指定要获取和修改的数据行
def user_edit(request, nid):
    user = models.UserInfo.objects.filter(id=nid).first()
    if request.method == "GET":
        form = UserForm(instance=user)
        return render(request, "user_edit.html", {"form": form})
    form = UserForm(data=request.POST, instance=user)
    if form.is_valid():
        #默认只提交用户输入值，可自定义额外值
        form.instance.update_time = datetime.now().strftime("%Y%m%d%H")
        form.save()
        return redirect("/user")
    return render(request, "user_edit.html", {"form": form})
```

    )

##### 钩子方法

```py
class UserForm(forms.ModelForm):

    # 已生成的字段会自带 clean_字段名 方法
    def clean_mobile(self):
        mobile_input = self.cleaned_data["mobile"]

        #判断数据长度
        if len(mobile_input) != 11:
            raise ValidationError("格式错误！")

        #判断数据是否存在,self.instance.pk获取ID,用于数据更新时排除自身
        exist = models.UserForm.objects.exclude(id=self.instance.pk).filter(mobile=mobile_input).exists()
        if exist:
            raise ValidationError("手机号已存在！")

        return mobile_input
```

## 中间件

settings.py中定义了中间件（类），自上到下顺序运行

```py
#settings.py

MIDDLEWARE = [
    'django.middleware.security.SecurityMiddleware',
    'django.contrib.sessions.middleware.SessionMiddleware',
    'django.middleware.common.CommonMiddleware',
    'django.middleware.csrf.CsrfViewMiddleware',
    'django.contrib.auth.middleware.AuthenticationMiddleware',
    'django.contrib.messages.middleware.MessageMiddleware',
    'django.middleware.clickjacking.XFrameOptionsMiddleware',
    'custom middleware 1',
    'custom middleware 2',
]
```

![image](data:image/png;base64,)

浏览器请求时顺序调用每个中间件的process_request，返回响应时逆序调用process_response

```py
from django.utils.deprecation import MiddlewareMixin

class M1(MiddlewareMixin):

    def process_request(self, request):
        # 如果方法中没有返回值，默认返回None，进程继续
        # 如果有返回值，只能使用HttpResponse、render、redirect
        print("M1 process_request")

    def process_response(self, request, response):
        print("M1 process_reponse")
        return response


class M2(MiddlewareMixin):

    def process_request(self, request):
        print("M2 process_request")

    def process_response(self, request, response):
        print("M2 process_response")
        return response

'''
M1 process_request
M2 process_request
M2 process_response
M1 process_response
'''
```

### process_request

```py
class custom_middleware(MiddlewareMixin):

    def process_request(self, request):
        # 如果方法中没有返回值，默认返回None，进程继续
        # 如果有返回值，则进程终止，转入该中间件的process_response返回至浏览器
        # 返回值只能使用HttpResponse、render、redirect
        return HttpResponse("无权访问")

    def process_response(self, request, response):
        return response
```

### 登录校验

编写登录中间件

```py
# app/middleware/auth.py

from django.utils.deprecation import MiddlewareMixin
from django.shortcuts import redirect


class AuthMiddleware(MiddlewareMixin):

    def process_request(self, request):
        # 排除不需要验证的页面
        if request.path_info == "/login":
            return

        login_info = request.session.get("info")
        if not login_info:
            return redirect('/login')
```

注册中间件

```py
#settings.py

MIDDLEWARE = [
    ...
    'app.middleware.auth.AuthMiddleware',
]
```

### 分页

```py
from django.utils.safestring import make_safe

    page = int(request.GET.get('page', 1))
    page_size = 10
    page_start = (page-1) * page_size
    page_end = page * page_size
    account = models.UserInfo.objects.filter(**data_list).order_by("-level")[page_start:page_end]

    info_count = models.SpecialAccount.objects.filter(**data_list).count()
    #ceil()向上取整
    page_num = ceil(info_count/page_size)

    page_list = []
    for i in range(1, page_num+1):
        ele = '<li><a href="/user/?page={}">{}</a></li>'.format(i, i)
        page_list.append(ele)
    page_str = mark_safe("".join(page_list))
```

封装好的分页组件

```py
from math import ceil
from django.utils.safestring import mark_safe
import copy

class Pagination(object):

    def __init__(self, request, queryset, page_param="page", page_size=10, page_num=2):

        page = request.GET.get(page_param, "1")
        if page.isdecimal():
            page = int(page)
        else:
            page = 1
        self.page = page
        self.page_size = page_size
        self.data_start = (page - 1) * page_size
        self.data_end = page * page_size
        self.page_data = queryset[self.data_start:self.data_end]
        self.data_count = queryset.count()
        self.page_count = ceil(self.data_count/page_size)

        #如果总页数小于等于要显示的页数
        if self.page_count <= page_num * 2 + 1:
            page_start = 1
            page_end = self.page_count
        #总页数大于要显示的页数
        else:
            #当前页数小于等于指定页数
            if page <= page_num:
                page_start = 1
                page_end = page_num * 2 + 1
            #当前页数大于指定页数
            elif page + page_num > self.page_count:
                page_start = page - 2
                page_end = self.page_count
            else:
                page_start = page - page_num
                page_end = page + page_num
        self.page_start = page_start
        self.page_end = page_end

        #请求中有多参数时获取参数然后修改
        #request.GET.setlist无法直接修改，故用copy
        url_param = copy.deepcopy(request.GET)
        url_param._mutable = True
        self.url_param = url_param

        page_list = []
        self.url_param.setlist(page_param, [1])
        page_pre = '<li><a href="/manage/?{}"><span aria-hidden="true"><</span></a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode())
        self.url_param.setlist(page_param, [page+1])
        page_next = '<li><a href="/manage/?{}"><span aria-hidden="true">></span></a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode())
        self.url_param.setlist(page_param, [1])
        page_first = '<li><a href="/manage/?{}" aria-label="Previous"><span aria-hidden="true">«</span></a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode())
        self.url_param.setlist(page_param, [self.page_count])
        page_last = '<li><a href="/manage/?{}" aria-label="Next"><span aria-hidden="true">»</span></a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode())
        page_jump = '<li><form style="float:left;" method="GET"><input style="float: left; inline-block; width: 54px; border-radius: 0px;" type="text" class="form-control" name="page"><button style="border-radius: 0px;" class="form-group btn btn-default" type="submit">跳转</button></form></li>'
        if page != 1:
            page_list.append(page_first)
            page_list.append(page_pre)
        for i in range(self.page_start, self.page_end + 1):
            self.url_param.setlist(page_param, [i])
            ele = '<li><a href="/manage/?{}">{}</a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode(), i)
            if i == page:
                ele = '<li class="active"><a href="/manage/?{}">{}</a></li>'.format(self.url_param.urlencode(), i)
            page_list.append(ele)
        if page != page_end:
            page_list.append(page_next)
            page_list.append(page_last)
        if page >= page_num * 2 + 1:
            page_list.append(page_jump)
        self.content = mark_safe("".join(page_list))
```

#content:    生成的html，常用
